Puppet module: rstatd

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages rstatd software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include rstatd              # Install and run rstatd with standard configurations.
include rstatd::disable     # Disable rstatd service.
include rstatd::disableboot # Disable rstatd service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include rstatd::absent      # Remove rstatd package.

DEPENDENCIES:
